      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in Clip 1.5.0</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Notes Tab</strong> — daily markdown editor with inline styling, keyword expansion, and preview</li>
          <li><strong>Floating Notes Panel</strong> — open with ⌥A for distraction-free writing alongside any app</li>
          <li><strong>Compact Icon Titlebar</strong> — tab icons inline with traffic lights, hover tooltips</li>
          <li><strong>Bundled CLI</strong> — clip command-line tool installs on first launch</li>
          <li><strong>Quick Look Extension</strong> — .clip vault files preview in Finder</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
